

Hotel Reviews:

Welcome to the Hotel Reviews project! This web application allows users to comment on and rate their dining experiences at various hotels.

Table of Contents:

Features
Technologies Used
Installation
Usage
Support and Contact
License


Features
Post a Comment: Share your thoughts on meals enjoyed at hotels.
Upload an Image: Add photos of your dishes to enhance your reviews.
Rate Your Experience: Provide a rating to help others gauge the quality.
Specify the Restaurant: Clearly identify the restaurant where the meal was had.
Edit/Delete Comments: Easily manage your feedback.


Technologies Used
HTML: For structure and content.
CSS: For styling and layout.
JavaScript: For interactivity and functionality.
db.json: For data storage.

Installation:
Clone the resipitory on:
https://github.com/Manu88x/project-phase-1-0-1

acess this site on:
https://manu88x.github.io/project-phase-1-0-1/

Usage
To post a review, fill in the required fields: comment, image, rating, and restaurant name.
After submitting, your review will appear on the page.
You can edit or delete your comments at any time.
